title: Easiest raid
author: Saren_Solaris
pages:
#- Day 1, After a failed§0
§0attack on the channers, Ive been pearled and banished to the end. The litteral end of things. So Ive decided to tell a story about My journey for everyone willing to read. Its not that interesting really but hey, What else is there 
#- to do really when Youre in the end of all things. The God of this realm was kind enough to give me books to write about My journey. So this is how it all began.§0
§0
§0---> next page
#- It all began with a calling from the realm of Reddit, A place of mysterious people judges one another by the recognition / upvotes they get on their comments or rather "contributions" weird concept really when You think about it. I mean what was it like
#- for the first human being to drink cow milk? Like how fucking crazy is that? Or the first person to eat chicken eggs. To the first human being to do it. I thank you, For without those massives balls, Humans could never have evolved beyond the apes that 
#- they where back then§0
§0Now We´re just smarter apes, Anyway doesnt matter, Back to reddit, A friend found a server called CivCraft and thats how my journey began......§0
§0
§0--> Chapter 2
#- Time passed, I saw the rules of this server, I dreamed about taking over, Raiding to My hearts content, I managed to piss off and raid a few cunts, Felt great, FELT ALL MIGHTY AND POWERFUL MUAHAHAHA, John got greedy and got carried away, I tried
#- to rescue my dumb friend but failed in my endeavor´s. I am now imprisoned for being a raider scumbag. §0
§0
§0I now seek My old friends to free me out, Many answered and now on their way to aid my call, Where we will take back what is ours, THE LAND OF THE FREE
#- and now I found your chest room, gg. Rekt noobs, ez PROT IV
#- 